   high-temperature (T = 800-3000 K) spectra have been performed in order
   to validate the databank. Comparisons of CDSD-1000 with other
   high-temperature databanks HITEMP, HITELOR, and EM2C are also given.
   CDSD-1000 is able to reproduce observed spectra in a more satisfactory
   way than the high-resolution databank HITEMP for temperatures higher
